Class ManagedCachingConnectionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.jms.connection.SingleConnectionFactory
      • org.springframework.jms.connection.CachingConnectionFactory
        • fr.xebia.springframework.jms.ManagedCachingConnectionFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ManagedCachingConnectionFactoryMBean, javax.jms.ConnectionFactory, javax.jms.ExceptionListener, javax.jms.QueueConnectionFactory, javax.jms.TopicConnectionFactory, Aware, BeanNameAware, DisposableBean, InitializingBean, SelfNaming

    public class ManagedCachingConnectionFactory
extends CachingConnectionFactory
implements ManagedCachingConnectionFactoryMBean, BeanNameAware, SelfNaming

    Subclass of CachingConnectionFactory to expose key attributes and operations via JMX.

    Most of the JMX exposition is done via the ManagedCachingConnectionFactoryMBean.

    Author:
    Cyrille Le Clerc
